metadata.name: The Struggle
metadata.description:
The entanglement is strong. 
Metanomicon is a collection of digital fine art taking you to the undergrounds of the birth of the Metaworld. As a wanderer diving into the womb of a new digital order ruled by human desires of possession, you will discover wonders and horrors of the human psyche entangled with digital and machine.

The purchase of this NFT will unlock the minting of the next one in the collection. The collection is a story in the making and you can be a part of it.

Digital Fine Art.
Nightmare rendered at 3240 x 5760 pixels
